  <acronym>COT</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Targeting Lower Arterial Oxygen Saturations to Reduce Oxygen Toxicity and Oxidative Stress in Very Preterm Infants: The Canadian Oxygen Trial (COT)</official_title>
